name: Listened to Chapter #5: Whipple Made Me Do It

content.html:
Orange Bowl BoysChapter #5: Whipple Made Me Do ItShow NotesThis episode was hijacked by #12…Jacory Harris! It’s all him with 5 Questions tagged at the end. So many great moments in this episode. Get ready to relive the 2008 #1 recruiting class with it’s leader in this episode which will certainly be a fan favorite.SportsPodcastAwards.com has us as finalists in 2 categories: College Sports Podcast of the Year (Orange Bowl Boys) and Comedy Sports Podcast of the Year (Benched). We’d appreciate your votes! Just go to the website and click on us! ThanksLastly, we have a HUGE party happening SATURDAY NIGHT at Tank Brewing in Miami with our boy TVD. All the details are in this episode. Hope to see you there!Sponsors: Ed Morse Automotive Group, BeatinTheBookie.com, DraftKings & CaneswearOrange Bowl Boys are owned and produced by OBB Media Inc. You can visit us online at www.obbmediainc.com. Copyright 2022.
